===Etymology===
[[Macedonia|Macedon (ia)]] + [[-ian]]

=== Noun ===
'''Macedonian''' ([[Macedonians]])

#An inhabitant or a resident of the Republic of Macedonia, the Macedonian Province in Greece, or Bulgarian Macedonia.
#A Slavic language spoken in The Republic of Macedonia, Greece, and Bulgaria.

